  "rawMarkdown" : "---\nsource: https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/System\/Errno\/canceled\ncrawled: 2026-03-10T22:03:37Z\n---\n\n# canceled\n\n**Type Property**\n\nOperation canceled.\n\n## Declaration\n\n```swift\nstatic var canceled: Errno { get }\n```\n\n## Discussion\n\nThe scheduled operation was canceled.\n\nThe corresponding C error is `ECANCELED`.\n\n## General Errors\n\n- **badMessage**: Bad message.\n- **illegalByteSequence**: Illegal byte sequence.\n- **noData**: No message available.\n- **noMessage**: No message of desired type.\n- **noSuchPolicy**: No such policy registered.\n- **notPermitted**: Operation not permitted.\n- **notRecoverable**: State not recoverable.\n- **outputQueueFull**: Interface output queue is full.\n- **tooManyReferences**: Too many references: can’t splice.\n- **tooManyUsers**: Too many users.\n\n",
